  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators are looking for volunteers who have a history of Major Depressive Disorder,
      the Winter Blues, or Seasonal Affective Disorder or healthy volunteers who do not have a
      history of these disorders for a research study on genetics.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The investigators are looking for volunteers who have a history of Major Depressive Disorder,
      the Winter Blues, or Seasonal Affective Disorder or healthy volunteers who do not have a
      history of these disorders for a research study on genetics. Participation involves one 2-3
      hour visit involving two diagnostic interviews, DNA collection, and questionnaires.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
